items.title: Trump and Putin to meet in coming days, Kremlin aide says
items.description: Expectations for a ceasefire between Moscow and Kyiv are muted, despite the US president's threat of sweeping sanctions.

items.title: Two Ghanaian ministers die in helicopter crash, along with six others
items.description: The authorities have not confirmed the cause of the crash, described as a "national tragedy".

items.title: 'Fake nurse' arrested in Florida after seeing more than 4,000 patients
items.description: A police investigation into Autumn Bardisa was launched due to concerns about her qualifications.

items.title: United Airlines passengers in US delayed after tech glitch halts flights
items.description: The company said late on Wednesday that its flights were no longer grounded, but that disruption was ongoing.

items.title: Payout for mother wrongfully jailed over babies' deaths 'inadequate' - lawyer
items.description: Kathleen Folbigg was freed in 2023 after a review found there was reasonable doubt she killed her babies.
